{"tid":1256167,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應美國安全顧慮   大疆擬美國生產無人機","createTime":"2019-06-25T00:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T03:53:31.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e14951ce553ea7f0b894e9e6bab6f3d19dec295","tid":1256167,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"回應美國安全顧慮 大疆擬美國生產無人機<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2172273\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2172273&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443vZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=ea195b63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2172273</a><br />\n<br />\n全球最大商用無人機製造商、中國深圳大疆創新科技(DJI Technology)宣布，計劃改裝美國加州現有倉庫，成為旗下Mavic 2 Enterprise Dual無人機的組裝廠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大疆指出，新安排有助拓展在美國的業務，以及為美國客戶提供更佳服務。大疆創新提及，根據美國海關的裁決，只要是在美國組裝，該款無人機將符合《美國貿易協議法》，令到美國政府部門可購買相關產品。<br />\n<br />\n上周，有美國國會議員與保安專家在國會參議院附屬委員會的聽證會上，敦促華府限制大疆創新產品的銷售，因為此舉危及美國人的個人私隱，以及產生國家安全顧慮。美國國會已經通過法案附件方式，限制軍方購買中國製造的無人機。"},{"pid":"86563e8c728c069fcb656b7ab2f3394d1a15f0d2","tid":1256167,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b3cf878c3beb0dd9f9ff5571647be305315b80","tid":1256167,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db34f28d1d926650e0c1a153ef3ec05e27654db1","tid":1256167,"uid":192052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"愛國去咗邊？去人國家生產<br />\n<br />\n中國有咩比唔上美國 又人工平 物料又平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb0f8b3536753e48e2d8582a4a8f9217ac32112","t